high_descs: Turn right and walk to the right side of the black dresser.
Pick up the pen that's in front of the plant.
Turn right and walk around the bed to the night stand.
Put the pen on the night stand in front of the lamp.
Walk back over to the other side of the room, and walk to the dresser on the left.
Pick up the pen to the left of the yellow container.
Walk back over to the night stand on the other side of the room.
Put the pen down on the night stand behind the first pen.
anns.task_desc: Move two pens to the night stand.

high_descs: Turn to the right and face the brown dresser.
Pick up the pen from the right side of the dresser.
Carry the pen and turn around. Past the bed, turn right and find the small dresser.
Place the pen on the dresser to the left side.
Turn around and then left past the bed. Turn left again and find the tall dresser.
Pick up the pen from the top of the tall dresser.
Carry the pen and turn to the right. Turn right again to find the small dresser beside the bed.
Place the pen on the small dresser, on top of the other pen.
anns.task_desc: Move two pens to a small dresser.

high_descs: Turn to your right and go past the bed, to the dresser across from you.
Pick up the pen, in front of the plant, on the right side of the dresser.
Turn around and go past the bed, then make a right and go to the night stand on the left side of the bed,
Place the pen in front of the lamp, near the edge of the night stand.
Turn around and go just past the bed, turn left and go to the end of the bed again, then make another left and go to the second dresser on your right.
Grab the pen on the dresser to the right of the bowl.
Turn to your right and go towards the door, then make a right and go to the end of the bed, then turn right again and go back to the night stand.
Place the pen behind the other pen, on the night stand.
anns.task_desc: Put two pens on the night stand.
